The American Stock Exchange said, aspreviously reported, that Bear Stearns and Co &lt;BSC> haspurchased &lt;W. Damm, M. Frank and Co>, a specialist unit on theAmex trading floor.    Amex said the unit, which trades stocks and options issmall in comparison to other specialist units. The personel andoperations remain the same, the exchange added.    The price was not disclosed.    A specialist unit is authorized by a stock exchange to dealas an agent for other brokers to keep a stable market in one ormore particular stocks. Reuter&#3;